{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "servicehub-otp-auth-v2",
    "name": "ServiceHub — OTP Auth + Booking API",
    "description": "Complete API collection for ServiceHub Flutter App.\n\n**Auth Flow:**\n1. Check Mobile → if exists, OTP sent\n2. Register → if new user, OTP sent\n3. Verify OTP → get Bearer Token ← Token auto-saved as {{token}}\n4. Use Bearer Token for protected routes\n5. Logout → token revoked\n\n**Booking Request Flow (after login):**\n6. Submit Booking Request → Admin mein pending request aayegi\n7. Get My Requests → User ki sabhi requests\n\n**Booking Flow (after login):**\n8. Get Add-ons → Available add-on services ki list\n9. Estimate Price → Booking create karne se pehle price check karo\n10. Create Booking → Confirmed booking banao\n11. Get My Bookings → Sabhi bookings fetch karo\n12. Get Booking Detail → Kisi ek booking ki detail\n13. Cancel Booking → Booking cancel karo\n\n**Base URL:** {{base_url}} = http://127.0.0.1:8000\n**OTP (Dummy):** 123456 (always)\n**Token:** auto-set after Verify OTP",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "base_url",
      "value": "http://127.0.0.1:8000",
      "type": "string",
      "description": "Laravel dev server URL. Change if hosted elsewhere."
    },
    {
      "key": "token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string",
      "description": "Bearer token — auto-filled after Verify OTP"
    },
    {
      "key": "booking_id",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string",
      "description": "Last created booking ID — auto-filled after Create Booking"
    }
  ],
